text: With Animals is the second collaborative studio album by American singer- songwriter Mark Lanegan and English multi-instrumentalist Duke Garwood. It was released on August 24, 2018 through Heavenly Recordings. ==Track listing== ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" |- ! Chart (2018) !
